creator: Onus Ant
descriptionHtml:
TopperMate : Quality study materials to enhance your education✍🏻.

The main goal is to provide best study material🧑🏻‍💼 to help your regular study 🙋🏽‍♂️ . We provide Lecture's video and Chapter's PDF ( hand written notes ).

🧑🏻‍🎓Everything according to New Education Policy 2020.

(Applicable) Study materials are available in both, English and Hindi medium.

At present, (Applicable) Study materials are available for Rajasthan Board but various common topics are available for other Boards like CBSE, NCERT, etc.

🤷‍♂️Beginning from Rajasthan Board, our vision is to cover all India Boards in near future.

🙋🏻‍♂️ TopperMate ensure 100% privacy for its user(Students)
Your personal information will never be collected in any condition. But to personalize the app according to your requirement, your academic details can be asked, which are kept safe inside the app's internal database and will never be shared with remote database hence none but only TopperMate app present in your device can utilize this information.
descriptionShort: TopperMate does not teach you, it provides study material for better learning.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Updated User Interface
Minimal design for ease of use
Switch account page added
Now you can switch to different account with only single click
Bugs fixed

rather than every notification.
